#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an6.83"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.83:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.83:0.2"
msgid "8. Arahattavagga "
msgstr "8. Perfection "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.83:0.3"
msgid "83. Aggadhammasutta "
msgstr "83. The Best Thing "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an6.83:1.1"
msgid "“Chahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu abhabbo aggaṃ dhammaṃ arahattaṃ sacchikātuṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, a mendicant with six qualities can’t realize the best thing, perfection. "

msgctxt "an6.83:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi chahi? "
msgstr "What six? "

msgctxt "an6.83:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu assaddho hoti, ahiriko hoti, anottappī hoti, kusīto hoti, duppañño hoti, kāye ca jīvite ca sāpekkho hoti. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant is faithless, shameless, imprudent, lazy, and witless. And they’re concerned with their body and their life. "

msgctxt "an6.83:1.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, chahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu abhabbo aggaṃ dhammaṃ arahattaṃ sacchikātuṃ. "
msgstr "A mendicant with these six qualities can’t realize the best thing, perfection. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.434, sc2
msgctxt "an6.83:2.1"
msgid "Chahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu bhabbo aggaṃ dhammaṃ arahattaṃ sacchikātuṃ. "
msgstr "A mendicant with six qualities can realize the best thing, perfection. "

msgctxt "an6.83:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi chahi? "
msgstr "What six? "

msgctxt "an6.83:2.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu saddho hoti, hirīmā hoti, ottappī hoti, āraddhavīriyo hoti, paññavā hoti, kāye ca jīvite ca anapekkho hoti. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant is faithful, conscientious, prudent, energetic, and wise. And they have no concern for their body and their life. "

msgctxt "an6.83:2.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, chahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu bhabbo aggaṃ dhammaṃ arahattaṃ sacchikātun”ti. "
msgstr "A mendicant with these six qualities can realize the best thing, perfection.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.83:2.5"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

